# The LOOSE Python source (ADR 0006c, laimk-hse.5): bare, unpinned package names —
# resolvable but NOT lock-grade. dustcastle resolves this ONCE via
# `uv pip compile --generate-hashes requirements.in -o requirements.txt`, producing
# a VISIBLE, hash-pinned requirements.txt (the committed artifact), after which the
# build runs pure/offline through the pip-FOD. Pure-Python, wheel-only deps so the
# nixpkgs python in the FOD downloads them regardless of the compiling interpreter.
idna
urllib3
